### CarrotCakeCMS Headless REST API — VS Code REST Client
### Install: humao.rest-client extension
### Usage: Update @baseUrl, @clientId, @clientSecret, @siteId below, then click "Send Request"

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@clientId = dev-client
@clientSecret = my-super-secret
@siteId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

# -------------------------------------------
# Step 1: Obtain a token (run this first)
# Copy the token value from the response into @token below
# -------------------------------------------

### 1a. Token — valid credentials
# @name tokenRequest
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": "{{clientId}}",
  "clientSecret": "{{clientSecret}}"
}

###

# -------------------------------------------
# After running the token request above,
# set @token to the value from data.token:
# -------------------------------------------
@token = {{tokenRequest.response.body.$.data.token}}

### 1b. Token — invalid credentials (expect 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": "{{clientId}}",
  "clientSecret": "WRONG_SECRET"
}

### 1c. Token — missing clientId (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientSecret": "{{clientSecret}}"
}

# -------------------------------------------
# Pages
# -------------------------------------------

### 2a. List all pages (default pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/pages?siteId={{siteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2b. List pages — page 2, pageSize 5
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/pages?siteId={{siteId}}&page=2&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2c. Get page by slug — published (expect 200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/pages?siteId={{siteId}}&slug=/about-us
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2d. Get page by slug — non-existent (expect 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/pages?siteId={{siteId}}&slug=/this-page-does-not-exist
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2e. Get page — no token (expect 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/pages?siteId={{siteId}}&slug=/about-us

# -------------------------------------------
# Posts
# -------------------------------------------

### 3a. List all posts (no filters)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/posts?siteId={{siteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3b. List posts filtered by category slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/posts?siteId={{siteId}}&category=news
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3c. List posts filtered by tag slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/posts?siteId={{siteId}}&tag=featured
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3d. List posts filtered by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/posts?siteId={{siteId}}&dateFrom=2025-01-01&dateTo=2025-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3e. List posts — category AND tag AND date range (AND logic)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/posts?siteId={{siteId}}&category=news&tag=featured&dateFrom=2025-01-01&dateTo=2025-12-31&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3f. List posts — out-of-range page (expect 200 with empty data array)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/posts?siteId={{siteId}}&page=9999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3g. List posts — invalid dateFrom format (expect 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/posts?siteId={{siteId}}&dateFrom=not-a-date
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3h. Get single post by slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/posts?siteId={{siteId}}&slug=/blog/2025/01/hello-world
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# -------------------------------------------
# Navigation
# -------------------------------------------

### 4a. Navigation tree for site (expect hierarchical JSON)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/navigation?siteId={{siteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4b. Navigation — no siteId on multi-site (expect 400 if multiple sites)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/navigation
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4c. Navigation — non-existent siteId (expect 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/navigation?siteId=ffffffff-ffff-ffff-ffff-ffffffffffff
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# -------------------------------------------
# Snippets
# -------------------------------------------

### 5a. Get snippet by name (expect 200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/snippets?siteId={{siteId}}&name=promo-banner
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5b. Get snippet — non-existent name (expect 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/snippets?siteId={{siteId}}&name=does-not-exist
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5c. Get snippet — missing name parameter (expect 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/snippets?siteId={{siteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# -------------------------------------------
# Widget Zones
# -------------------------------------------

### 6a. Get widget zone for a page (expect 200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/widgetzones?siteId={{siteId}}&pageSlug=/home&zone=sidebar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6b. Widget zone — alternative zone name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/widgetzones?siteId={{siteId}}&pageSlug=/home&zone=footer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6c. Widget zone — page slug not found (expect 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/widgetzones?siteId={{siteId}}&pageSlug=/nonexistent-page&zone=sidebar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6d. Widget zone — missing zone parameter (expect 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/headless/widgetzones?siteId={{siteId}}&pageSlug=/home
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# -------------------------------------------
# Health check
# -------------------------------------------

### 7a. Health check (expect {"status":"Healthy"})
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
